    public enum Role
extends Enum<Role>
implements Principal
    Defines the available roles of a StaffMember.
    See Also:
    UserProfile.getRole()

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      BARKEEPER
      AccessControlGroup of a barkeeper who is responsible for taking orders for drinks at the bar as well as serving and billing them.
      CHIEF
      AccessControlGroup of a chief on the restaurant who can manage the master-data such as offers, products, and other StaffMembers.
      COOK
      AccessControlGroup of a cook who works in the kitchen and can see the orders with their positions.
      WAITER
      AccessControlGroup of a waiter who manages the table states, takes orders at the tables and serves drinks and the prepared food from the kitchen.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • COOK

        public static final Role COOK
        AccessControlGroup of a cook who works in the kitchen and can see the orders with their positions. He prepares the menus and side-dishes and can mark order-positions as prepared.

      • WAITER

        public static final Role WAITER
        AccessControlGroup of a waiter who manages the table states, takes orders at the tables and serves drinks and the prepared food from the kitchen. Further, he is responsible for billing the payments of orders, etc.

      • BARKEEPER

        public static final Role BARKEEPER
        AccessControlGroup of a barkeeper who is responsible for taking orders for drinks at the bar as well as serving and billing them.

      • CHIEF

        public static final Role CHIEF
        AccessControlGroup of a chief on the restaurant who can manage the master-data such as offers, products, and other StaffMembers.
